  /**
   * A {@link BiMap} backed by two {@link HashMap} instances. This implementation
   * allows null keys and values. A {@code HashBiMap} and its inverse are both
   * serializable.
   *
   * @author Mike Bostock
   * @since 2 (imported from Google Collections Library)
